NAME
    App::sqltree - implementation of the sqltree command

VERSION
    0.0.5_1 (2013-06-12)

SYNOPSIS
        # Via OptArgs
        use OptArgs 'dispatch';
        dispatch(qw/run App::sqltree/);

        # Or directly
        use App::sqltree;

        my @sql = App::sqltree::run(
            {
                no_print => 1,
                driver   => 'SQLite',
                table    => 'items',
                pk       => 'id',
                parent   => 'parent_id',
                type     => 'integer',
            }
        );

DESCRIPTION
    This is the implementation module for the sqltree command.

SEE ALSO
    OptArgs, sqltree

